reviewText: What a great workout. I liked it so much I ordered other 3 DVDs.
I think it's:  not too heavy; not too light; just right!  I will use this a few times a week atleast!

An excellent workout! In only 30 minutes, you are able to work all major muscle groups, as well as improve flexibility and balance. The workout is challenging and very rewarding! I would recommend this DVD to anyone.
